-- U.K. to Sell Early Phase 3 Carbon Permits on Nov. 21 and Dec. 5
-- B y   A l e s s a n d r o   V i t e l l i
-- 2012-09-28T10:28:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-09-28/u-k-to-sell-early-phase-3-carbon-permits-on-nov-21-and-dec-5.html
The U.K. will hold two sales of so-
called early Phase 3 European Union carbon allowances on Nov. 21
and Dec. 5, the European Commission said in a statement on its
website.  The sales will be carried out by ICE Futures  Europe , which
has been approved by the Commission to hold auctions in the
third phase of the blocâ€™s carbon market, which begins in 2013.
ICE will also hold two sales of EU aviation permits on Nov. 26
and Dec. 10, the Commission said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
